**Shubro's 1% Daily Coding Growth Plan**

---

**Why:** To become job-ready, build confidence, and create real-world projects (like your billing app) ‚Äî even with limited time and energy.

**Goal:** Improve 1% daily in web development (MERN stack + real-world thinking)

**Time Required:** 30 to 60 minutes daily

