---

### üìö Step-by-Step Daily Plan

**1. Learn (10-15 min)**
- Watch a video or read docs/blog about **one concept** (example: `map()`, `POST API`)
- Take a tiny note or screenshot to remember it

**2. Build (20-30 min)**
- Add or fix **just one feature or bug** in your app
- Apply what you just learned
- Even one small thing counts!

**3. Reflect (5-10 min)**
- Write: "What I learned today, what I did, what I‚Äôll do tomorrow"
- Track in notebook, Google Doc, or this file

---

### ‚ú® Weekly Mini-Challenge
- **Day 1-5:** Learn + Build + Reflect
- **Day 6:** Refactor or clean up code (naming, formatting, better logic)
- **Day 7 (Friday or Sunday):** Review your progress, plan 1 goal for next week

